sentences: Lilya Efimovna Zilberstein (Russian: Лилия Ефимовна Зильберштейн; born 19 April 1965) is a Russian-born German pianist.
Born in Moscow and educated at the Gnessin State Musical College (1971–88), she rose to prominence after winning the 1987 Concorso Busoni.
Born in Moscow and educated at the Gnessin State Musical College (1971–88), she rose to prominence after winning the 1987 Concorso Busoni.
She settled in Hamburg two years later, where she still lives with her husband and her two sons, Daniel and Anton.
She has been teaching at the Accademia Musicale Chigiana in Siena since 2011.
